{
  "stem": "27129.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one of the days, you know, they came out with the-- it wasn't a law, but it was a-- how do you say it in English?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Like an edict?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Huh?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not a statement.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's a-- they can shoot you on the spot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What is that?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You had to put on the yellow band, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To identify yourself.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You didn't have to identify yourself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They already knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, they beat up people in the street, whoever wanted to.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, it was a horrible sight.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one of the mornings, you know, we got up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was in the marketplace, they hung three people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I figured if the government can hang people in the streets, you know, nothing good you can expect from a government like that.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that happened in a day where it used to be a holiday for the Polish people, like the 4th of July in the United States, when the Poles obtained freedom.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my brother and I decided-- but because the third brother, we didn't know where he is, because-- What was his name, the other brother who left?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Aaron, the oldest brother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Was Henry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mm-hm.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
